duties_responsibilities.duty: Evaluate and analyze content like images and videos to improve the accuracy of search results.
Contribute to enhancing the web browsing experience for users by providing feedback on search engine results.
Participate in the collection and labeling of images, text, speech, audio, video, and other data for AI systems.
Contribute to providing reliable training data for technology, automotive, financial services, retail, healthcare, and governments.
Pass a qualification exam to become a Search Engine Analyst.

education_certification.credential: High school diploma required, Bachelor's degree preferred.
